    "title": "京东开放平台恶意铺品细则",
    "followRuleId": "1287356754237198336",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0pt; padding: 0pt; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; text-indent: 0pt; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2; font-family: 等线;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.【违规定义】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">恶意铺品：以挤占平台流量、误导消费者为核心目的，通过恶意使用批量发布工具、搬运他人商品、重复上架、信息造假等不当方式，上架大量无实质售卖价值、信息虚假、低质冗余的无效商品，导致店铺无效商品数量大幅激增、平台商品供给质量整体下滑，进而造成商品价格偏离合理区间、消费者权益与购物体验无保障，严重扰乱平台正常运营秩序的经营行为。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.</span></strong><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【处理措施】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">京东有权根据违规情节严重程度，对涉事商家店铺及关联店铺采取预警、开具违约单、管控、限权、关店等处理措施。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">管控措施</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">包括但不限于<span style=\"color: #000000;\">：<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">违规商品下架且限制重新上架、限制店铺内商品发布数量上限、限制每日新发商品数、<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">全店商品下架</span>、全店商品流量降权 / 屏蔽、限制提报平台营销活动、加收风险保证金、<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">扣除店铺资金（包括保证金、货款等）</span>、限制关联品类商品上架；</span> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">限权措施</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">包括但不限于：限制新品标识申请、限制厂自模式使用权限、限制 ISV 工具部分功能使用、限制商品信息批量编辑权限。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 32px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.【规则解读】</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.1为什么对恶意铺品进行管控？</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大量无效低质商品在信息真实性、商品质量、服务标准、履约及售后保障等关键环节均无有效保障，严重侵害消费者得购物体验，违背平台 &ldquo;保障消费者权益&rdquo; 的核心原则</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大量无效低质商品挤占平台公共资源，降低运营效率，影响平台秩序与可持续发展。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">恶意铺货商家无需投入实质经营成本，通过批量铺货抢占流量曝光等核心资源，规避正常经营竞争，既破坏了平台公平竞争环境，也直接侵犯了合规商家的公平竞争权益。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.2什么行为会被判定为恶意铺品？</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">判定为恶意铺品的情况包括但不限于：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">批量复制京东平台内及平台外他人店铺的商品标题、主图、详情页等核心信息，仅做轻微修改（如替换关键词、调整图片顺序）或完全照搬后上架销售；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）大</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">量上架重复 / 高度相似商品、信息虚假（如材质 / 规格 / 功能标注与实际不符）、关键信息缺失、详情页空白 / 杂乱，或盗用他人原创素材、无实质售卖价值的无效商品</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">店铺商品总量显著超出同类合规店铺正常水平，缺乏有效运营动作（如无商品信息维护、售后响应低效等），动销率低，且无法提供稳定货源证明（如供货协议、库存凭证等）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大量商品标价显著高于同品类同规格合规商品合理价格区间，且无成本上涨、独家授权等正当理由，同时伴随商品信息批量复制、无效铺货等特征。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">通过多账号、关联店铺、关联主体协同铺货，大量上架无效商品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.3商家因恶意铺品被开具违约单后，可提供哪些材料进行申诉？</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家在申诉时可以提供包括但不限于商品信息原创 / 合法授权证明（如设计底稿、授权协议、知识产权登记证书等）、稳定货源证明（如供货协议、库存凭证、采购发票等）、商品价格合理性依据（如成本核算表、市场定价说明、独家授权证明等）、无效商品整改完成截图、店铺有效运营记录（如商品信息维护记录、售后响应记录、动销率提升情况、广告计划运行情况等）；平台将结合材料进行综合判断。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.4商家被判定为恶意铺品违规后，有哪些方式可进行整改？</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">全面清理违规商品，下架或删除全部无效商品。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">规范商品信息发布，补充完善商品标题、主图、详情页等核心信息，确保关键属性（规格、材质、功能等）真实完整，若使用其他平台商品信息需提供合法授权证明。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3）</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">优化店铺运营质量，控制店铺商品总量在同类合规店铺合理范围，通过完善商品信息、提升客服响应效率、售后满意度等提升动销率等经营指标。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.附则</span></strong></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.1京东可根据平台运营及生态治理需要，随时调整本恶意铺品治理规则，并以公告形式向商家公示，公示后即生效。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.2</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌恶意铺品及违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有约定的，适用本规则；本规则尚无约定的，京东有权酌情处理，但不免除商家应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议；若商家服务协议约定的违约金金额高于本规则约定的，京东有权适用协议约定。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 12pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.3</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本规则于 2025年11月28日修订，于 2025年12月5日生效。</span></p>",
